</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">通常是</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">0-18岁</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">身体符合条件，无年龄要求</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">投资额度</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">每个孩子终身投资额不得多于</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">5万元，否则将有政府罚款</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">与家庭资产状况相关，没有投资上限</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">投资方向</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">个人计划投资可以根据风险偏好在股票、基金、债券、定存中选择投资产品，团体计划由教育基金公司帮助投资，主要以稳健型债券为主</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">保险公司决定投资方向，通常以固定收益的投资类产品为主</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
