</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">没有体检要求</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">通常</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">16岁以下没有体检要求，有可能会调阅家庭医生医疗记录</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">取款要求</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">孩子需要上大学（包括全职或兼职）方能享有政府福利补贴，否则政府福利部分将退回。在开户后的第</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">35年，必须取款。</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-right: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; padding: 3.75pt 7.5pt 3.75pt 7.5pt;">
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">只要有现金价值即可取款，作为一项中长期投资，通常在</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #3f3f3f;">20年甚至更长时间以后取款。</span></p>
</td>
